 art of Masses women and a series of biographical/bibliographical sketches designed to aid other researchers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 0aAfrican literaturexStudy and teaching. 0aAuthors, American - 20th century - Biography. 0aFolklorezAfricavBibliography. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Women's Studies.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292780224423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292780224/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK